      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_cd26a19baceaac5f4975b6c3e37cb3c5">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The drawings are arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_7abee5aed27939bb9a6727eb6762676e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of pencil drawings of people and objects by Richard W. Arnold while a student at Yale. Although Arnold has created gay-themed art, the drawings in the collections do not contain any explicitly gay-themed drawings.</p>  
